I’ve struggled with pimples and blackheads since I was a teenager, so 2-weeks ago!! I joke, but only about the age, not the skin…living with complex skin was one of my biggest insecurities and can still be if my acne flairs up. A big zit is always there to say, “SURPRISE SYNTHIA” if I’m not on my cleansing game. That’s why the right routine is verrrrry important to me. Makeup removal is always super simple with @neutrogenacanada 
.
The double cleanse tackles stubborn makeup and leaves my skin cleansed before bed. I'm definitely packing their wipes and cleanser for my gigs this Summer, my pores will thank me later. 
.
With 2023 Pride just around the corner, celebrate with Neutrogena and show your skin some love. Whether you're rocking a fierce face or going au naturel, join me in embracing your true self with #Neutrogena! #AD

DRAGCON DUMP!!

Ever wonder how you create a drag supergroup? This summer, get ready for the unofficial story on how three queens from Vancouver became one of the biggest drag groups,  in THE B FACTOR. 

Get ready for Kendall Gender, Gia Metric & Synthia Kiss to take you on a journey of world famous trios as they become the ultimate drag group...THE BRATPACK. 

Tickets starting at $25.00 plus tax + s/c on sale Tuesday May 30th

Pre sale tickets available now at www.bratpackforever.com

Video by @synthiakiss

🌱🌍 Join me and @MetroVancouverBC this Summer making Superhabits: small actions that can make a big difference in reducing single-use items, like using reusable utensils. I gave out the cutest utensil sets to beachgoers who forget theirs, and now they can start Superhabits too! 💪🔄 #WhatsYourSuperhabit? Share yours and inspire others to join the movement. 🌎✨  #MetroVancouver #ZeroWaste
 
For tips and more visit Superhabits.ca. Let’s save the day with our small daily routines and protect our region and planet together. 🌟♻️ Remember, choosing reusable alternatives is always the best option. ♻️💚 Together, we can make a lasting impact! 🙌💙

🌈🍸Raise your glass and celebrate love, equality, and diversity with Iceberg Vodka! 🍸🌈
June is Pride Month, a time when we come together to honour and embrace the LGBTQ+ community. Iceberg Vodka believes in supporting love in all its beautiful forms, and it’s the perfect affordable vodka to have on hand to create any kind of cocktail. 🏳️‍🌈💙❤️🧡💛💚💜
Cheers to love, equality, and a world that embraces diversity!

#IcebergCocktailNight #IcebergVodka #CanadasVodka #PrideMonth #LoveIsLove #LGBTQ

Remember, it’s all about reducing and reusing, not just recycling and disposal. 🔄♻️
 
Tag your coworkers and share your favourite reusable coffee cup to inspire others. Together, we can create a sustainable workplace. Let’s make every coffee break count! ☕️💚
